            "body": "> Annoyingly these still surface in `checkhealth vim.lsp` warnings when _not_ using the old configs:\r\n\r\num... that is either a bug in the healthcheck, or something in your config is touching/loading the configs somehow.\r\n\r\nWe can merge this meanwhile though.",
